  "bodyHtml": "\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"paragraph\" style=\"text-align:justify;\"><font size=\"3\"><span style=\"\">The 46th Annual Festival du Voyageur held its Jigging and Fiddling Contest on February 21st and 22nd, 2015 at the Centre culturel franco-manitobain.</span></font><font size=\"3\"><span style=\"\"><br> To celebrate the 44th anniversary of the jigging and fiddling contests, l'Ensemble Folklorique de la Rivi</span><span id=\"selectionBoundary_1425137499814_14532931335270405\" class=\"rangySelectionBoundary\" style=\"line-height: 0; display: none;\">﻿</span><span style=\"\">è</span><span style=\"\">re-Rouge performed at the Jigging Contest and Michael Audette and Band entertained at the Fiddling Contest.</span></font><br><font size=\"3\"><span style=\"\">Please see results and image of winners below.</span></font><font size=\"3\"><span style=\"\"><br></span></font></div>  <div><div style=\"margin: 10px 0 0 -10px\"> <a href=\"/assets/uploads/1/9/6/9/19690537/festival_du_voyageur_results.pdf\"><img src=\"//www.weebly.com/weebly/images/file_icons/pdf.png\" width=\"36\" height=\"36\" style=\"float: left; position: relative; left: 0px; top: 0px; margin: 0 15px 15px 0; border: 0;\"></a><div style=\"float: left; text-align: left; position: relative;\"><table style=\"font-size: 12px; font-family: tahoma; line-height: .9;\"><tbody><tr><td colspan=\"2\"><b> festival_du_voyageur_results.pdf</b></td></tr><tr style=\"display: none;\"><td>File Size:  </td><td>17 kb</td></tr><tr style=\"display: none;\"><td>File Type:  </td><td> pdf</td></tr></tbody></table><a href=\"/assets/uploads/1/9/6/9/19690537/festival_du_voyageur_results.pdf\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Download File</a></div> </div>  <hr style=\"clear: both; width: 100%; visibility: hidden\"></div>  <div><div class=\"wsite-image wsite-image-border-medium \" style=\"padding-top:0;padding-bottom:5px;margin-left:0;margin-right:15px;text-align:left\"> <a href=\"/assets/uploads/1/9/6/9/19690537/8310983_orig.jpg\" rel=\"lightbox\" onclick=\"if (!lightboxLoaded) return false\"> <img src=\"/assets/uploads/1/9/6/9/19690537/8310983.jpg\" alt=\"Picture\" style=\"width:709;max-width:100%\"> </a> <div style=\"display:block;font-size:90%\">Winners of the Championship Class (from left): Marc Remillard - MC, Alex Kusturok - 1st place, Émilie Chartier - 2nd place, Jane Cory - 3rd place, Maria Cherwick - 4th place, Véronique Demers - 5th place, Kaitlyn Obedzinski - 6th place, Simon Reimer - 7th place, Monique &amp; André Chartier - Event Coordinators.</div> </div></div>\n\n\t\t",
